channel.title: Dodian server messes up after a while. Says Null
channel.description:
Here is just a part of the log when the server messes up. [code]Connection from XX.XX.XXX.XX:XXXXX [client-12-Identity]: Loading Process Completed [Regular player, lag: 16 ms] ClientHandler: Client null disconnected (XX.XX.XXX.XX) null null null[/code]
When that happens the server doesen't work. When people try to connect they just get a black loading screen. They can still see the chat but nothing comes up its all just black box.
Anyone know how to fix this?
